efault/files/styles/listing_image_medium/public/media/media/5ee1d44b4c53b108f5d08460962f307f133ad6e54e50744f72287cd09744cd_960_0.jpg?itok=lF7zQmWb')"> &nbsp;</div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h3 class="field-content"><a href="/articles/science-news/australian-tree-drug-kills-bacteria">Australian Tree Drug Kills Bacteria</a></h3></div><div class="views-field views-field-created"> <span class="field-content">16 September 2022</span></div><div class="views-field views-field-body"><div class="field-content"><p>Compounds capable of treating hard to heal wound infections have been isolated from a tree species in Australia</p></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-naked-discovery-podcast-ur-1"><div class="field-content"></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-naked-discovery-podcast-ur-2"><div class="field-content"></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-nodequeue-links"> <span class="field-content"></span></div></div></div><div class=" col-xs-12 col-lg-4"><div class="grid"><div class="views-field views-field-nothing"> <span class="field-content"><div class="views-field-term-node-tid"><a href="/articles/science-news">Science News</a> | <a href="/articles/science-news/biology">Biology</a> | <a href="/articles/science-news/medicine" class="active">Medicine</a> | <a href="/articles/science-news/space">Space</a></div></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-image"><div class="field-content"><div class="image-wrap image-opaque image-listing-md"><div class="image-field"><a href="/articles/science-news/lettuce-against-bone-density-loss"><div class="background-image-formatter" style="background-image: url('https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/styles/listing_image_medium/public/media/media/g3293633c9f5e3d37e526e6a96a1a0fb8995c82c146ff718c52e92f50caa9bd9840c41cbc24d98ecb79ca1645108862c4_1280.jpg?itok=xNhiMhJ9')"> &nbsp;</div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="views-