res can lead to big increases in healthy purchases and drops in sales of sweets.</p></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-naked-discovery-podcast-ur-1"><div class="field-content"></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-naked-discovery-podcast-ur-2"><div class="field-content"></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-nodequeue-links"> <span class="field-content"></span></div></div></div><div class="clearfix visible-lg"></div><div class=" col-xs-12 col-lg-4"><div class="grid"><div class="views-field views-field-nothing"> <span class="field-content"><div class="views-field-term-node-tid"><a href="/articles/science-news">Science News</a> | <a href="/articles/science-news/chemistry">Chemistry</a> | <a href="/articles/science-news/engineering">Engineering</a> | <a href="/articles/science-news/medicine" class="active">Medicine</a></div></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-image"><div class="field-content"><div class="image-wrap image-opaque image-listing-md"><div class="image-field"><a href="/articles/science-news/wireless-pacemaker-dissolves-when-done"><div class="background-image-formatter" style="background-image: url('https://www.thenakedscientists.com/sites/default/files/styles/listing_image_medium/public/media/media/57e6d6444a5ab108f5d08460962f307f133ad6e54e50744c7c287fd2924dcd_960.jpg?itok=m1LEUUNA')"> &nbsp;</div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-title-1"><h3 class="field-content"><a href="/articles/science-news/wireless-pacemaker-dissolves-when-done">Wireless pacemaker dissolves when done</a></h3></div><div class="views-field views-field-created"> <span class="field-content">13 July 2021</span></div><div class="views-field views-field-body"><div class="field-content"><p>A novel type of fully implantable temporary pacemaker has been developed that naturally absorbs into the body</p></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-naked-discovery-podcast-ur-1"><div class="field-